## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The reliance on secondary sources means that some nuances of the psychological motivations behind cheating may not be fully captured. Additionally, the dynamic nature of sports and societal attitudes towards cheating means that motivations can evolve, and newer studies may provide different insights.